IMPORTANT DISCLAIMER

This project is an academic and speculative reconstruction. It makes no claim
to be revealed scripture, an authoritative religious text, or a recovery of
any lost original Gospel or Injil. It is a scholarly and comparative exercise
in textual criticism, undertaken from an Islamic theological framework.

No part of this project should be presented, distributed, or understood as
divine revelation, prophetic hadith, or binding religious authority of any
kind. Any passage adapted, reconstructed, or rewritten herein is the product
of human reasoning, comparative textual analysis, and academic hypothesis,
not revelation.

Readers of all backgrounds -- Muslim, Christian, Jewish, secular -- are
encouraged to engage critically and consult qualified scholars in their own
traditions.
